#########################
Installing science3point0
#########################

=====================
for local development
=====================

science3point0 requires...
 - Wordpress 3.0 installation
 - MYSQL database

Getting a local copy running is easy. 

Set up a WP 3.0 multi user site.
Upload the contents of the plugins folder into wp-content/plugins/
Activate the plugins
Upload the science3point0 theme folder into wp-content/themes/
Activate the theme


You now have your own scientific community - Please use this to customise and add all things 'sciencey' or '3.0ey'



